<p>Are you looking for a Customer Service position with an expanding and innovative company? If so, <b>Guardian Protection Services </b>is hiring career-minded <b>Customer Service Representatives </b>for our location in <b>Tempe, AZ! </b>If you are interested in joining a world class Customer Service team, then</p>

<p><b>We want YOU to Apply Below Now!</b></p>

<p><a href="http://bullhorn.personified.com/client/jobInfoApplicationRespMgmt.action?EntityID=20112&amp;source=Craigslist_P" rel="nofollow">http://bullhorn.personified.com/client/jobInfoApplicationRespMgmt.action?EntityID=20112&amp;source=Craigslist_P</a></p>

<p><br>
<b>What we offer:</b></p>

<p>· Highly competitive salary with free/discounted services</p>

<p>· Medical, Dental, Vision</p>

<p>· Paid vacations, sick time, &amp; holidays</p>

<p>· 401(k)</p>

<p>· Long Term Disability</p>

<p>· Substantial internal growth opportunity</p>

<p>· Plus much, much more!</p>

<p>Read the responsibilities &amp; requirements below and <b>APPLY NOW</b> for immediate consideration!</p>

<p><b>Requirements:</b></p>

<p>The <b>Customer Service Representative </b>position requires:</p>

<p>· Previous customer service experience is required</p>

<p>· Previous call center experience is preferred, but not required</p>

<p>· Candidates fluent in Spanish are encouraged to apply</p>

<p>· Must be at least 18 years of age</p>

<p>· A high school diploma (Or GED equivalency)</p>

<p>· Must be able to pass an 8-week training course that runs from 7:30am-4:30pm, Monday-Friday</p>

<p>· Flexible schedules are very important as your shift can be anywhere from 6:00am-10:00pm, and weekend &amp; holiday availability is also required</p>

<p>· Ability to navigate multiple windows and programs at one time</p>

<p>· Must be able to type a minimum of 35 words per minute</p>

<p>· Drug screen &amp; background check will also be conducted</p>

<p>· Excellent communication and soft skills are a must</p>

<p><b>Responsibilities:</b></p>

<p>As a <b>Customer Service Representative </b>you are responsible for:</p>

<p>· Build excellent client relationships by placing proactive calls to ensure installations and service calls where satisfactory and met expectations</p>

<p>· Continually maintain a working knowledge of all company products, services and promotions</p>

<p>· Relentlessly demonstrate your enthusiasm, professionalism and integrity</p>

<p>· Assisting customers with technical support</p>

<p>· Will assist customers with testing of alarm systems</p>

<p><b>APPLY BELOW! We hope to hear from you soon!</b></p>

<p><a href="http://bullhorn.personified.com/client/jobInfoApplicationRespMgmt.action?EntityID=20112&amp;source=Craigslist_P" rel="nofollow">http://bullhorn.personified.com/client/jobInfoApplicationRespMgmt.action?EntityID=20112&amp;source=Craigslist_P</a></p>

<p><br>
<br>
</p>
    </section>

